  lines:
  - speaker: Yes
    line: 'You got me. I was following you. '
    SpriteRange: 6
  - speaker: You
    line: "Gotta make sure you don\u2019t go out killing anyone else."
    SpriteRange: 6
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: Oh? Do you truly believe I would do such without cause?
    SpriteRange: 6
  - speaker: YOu
    line: "I mean\u2026I wouldn\u2019t really put it past you."
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: 'My my. You have quite the mouth on you to be saying such a thing. '
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: Kuchisake-Onna
    line: However, I commend your honesty.
    SpriteRange: 6
